01:25:02.500 --> 01:25:04.500
to the managers of the middle

01:25:04.500 --> 01:25:06.500
or lower ranks.

01:25:06.500 --> 01:25:08.500
That is, people who lead

01:25:08.500 --> 01:25:10.500
the department and are responsible

01:25:10.500 --> 01:25:12.500
for specific areas of work,

01:25:12.500 --> 01:25:14.500
primarily group.

01:25:14.500 --> 01:25:16.500
The positional contribution here

01:25:16.500 --> 01:25:18.500
must be average in the market,

01:25:18.500 --> 01:25:20.500
otherwise it will not work,

01:25:20.500 --> 01:25:22.500
but it should not

01:25:22.500 --> 01:25:24.500
exhaust the entire amount of reward.

01:25:24.500 --> 01:25:26.500
It should be approximately 60-70%

01:25:26.500 --> 01:25:28.500
of the total reward of our employee.

01:25:28.500 --> 01:25:30.500
Prizes, yes, of course,

01:25:30.500 --> 01:25:32.500
monthly or quarterly,

01:25:32.500 --> 01:25:34.500
the rest 30-40%,

01:25:34.500 --> 01:25:36.500
and according to the results of the department.

01:25:36.500 --> 01:25:38.500
They must certainly take into account

01:25:38.500 --> 01:25:40.500
the result of the work of our employee

01:25:40.500 --> 01:25:42.500
precisely in the department

01:25:42.500 --> 01:25:44.500
as a manager,

01:25:44.500 --> 01:25:46.500
that is, how he managed

01:25:46.500 --> 01:25:48.500
his subordinates.

01:25:48.500 --> 01:25:50.500
Third, bonuses.

01:25:50.500 --> 01:25:52.500
They can be,

01:25:52.500 --> 01:25:54.500
but not so big.

01:25:54.500 --> 01:25:56.500
And it is very important,

01:25:56.500 --> 01:25:58.500
they may not be,

01:25:58.500 --> 01:26:00.500
everything can be limited by bonuses.

01:26:00.500 --> 01:26:02.500
But if we pay a bonus to such an employee,

01:26:02.500 --> 01:26:04.500
we demonstrate to him

01:26:04.500 --> 01:26:06.500
the importance of his personal work,

01:26:06.500 --> 01:26:08.500
his department for the company as a whole.

01:26:08.500 --> 01:26:10.500
The social package.

01:26:10.500 --> 01:26:12.500
This package is certainly necessary,

01:26:12.500 --> 01:26:14.500
but there is no need

01:26:14.500 --> 01:26:16.500
to adjust this package

01:26:16.500 --> 01:26:18.500
to the needs of this particular employee

01:26:18.500 --> 01:26:20.500
as in the previous case.

01:26:20.500 --> 01:26:22.500
It can be a general social package

01:26:22.500 --> 01:26:24.500
provided to everyone

01:26:24.500 --> 01:26:26.500
equal to him in position,

01:26:26.500 --> 01:26:28.500
probably according to the cafeteria system.

01:26:28.500 --> 01:26:30.500
The social package should be increased

01:26:30.500 --> 01:26:32.500
as a result of the experience,

01:26:32.500 --> 01:26:34.500
which increases the loyalty

01:26:34.500 --> 01:26:36.500
of our organization's employees,

01:26:36.500 --> 01:26:38.500
and according to the achieved results,

01:26:38.500 --> 01:26:40.500
it can also affect

01:26:40.500 --> 01:26:42.500
the growth of our employee.

01:26:48.500 --> 01:26:50.500
The next compensation plan,

01:26:50.500 --> 01:26:52.500
we call it a professional plan,

01:26:52.500 --> 01:26:54.500
is a plan for qualified specialists,

01:26:54.500 --> 01:26:56.500
first of all,

01:26:56.500 --> 01:26:58.500
engineering specialists,

01:26:58.500 --> 01:27:00.500
who do not manage other people,

01:27:00.500 --> 01:27:02.500
that is, they are not managers.

01:27:02.500 --> 01:27:04.500
Their task is,

01:27:04.500 --> 01:27:06.500
first of all,

01:27:06.500 --> 01:27:08.500
to provide uninterrupted

01:27:08.500 --> 01:27:10.500
functioning of equipment,

01:27:10.500 --> 01:27:12.500
mechanisms, inventions,

01:27:12.500 --> 01:27:14.500
and all that concerns

01:27:14.500 --> 01:27:16.500
the technical part of our enterprise,

01:27:16.500 --> 01:27:18.500
including, of course,

01:27:18.500 --> 01:27:20.500
IT specialists.

01:27:20.500 --> 01:27:22.500
The salary should be,

01:27:22.500 --> 01:27:24.500
again, medium in the market,

01:27:24.500 --> 01:27:26.500
not high,

01:27:26.500 --> 01:27:28.500
and not low either,

01:27:28.500 --> 01:27:30.500
and should be 70-80% of the reward.

01:27:30.500 --> 01:27:32.500
The remaining 20-30%

01:27:32.500 --> 01:27:34.500
of the reward

01:27:34.500 --> 01:27:36.500
should be received,

01:27:36.500 --> 01:27:38.500
of course, as a bonus,

01:27:38.500 --> 01:27:40.500
every month,

01:27:40.500 --> 01:27:42.500
but in this case,

01:27:42.500 --> 01:27:44.500
it should be received in full

01:27:44.500 --> 01:27:46.500
only if it fully fulfills

01:27:46.500 --> 01:27:48.500
the obligations imposed on it.

01:27:48.500 --> 01:27:50.500
If it makes mistakes,

01:27:50.500 --> 01:27:52.500
if there are errors,

01:27:52.500 --> 01:27:54.500
if there are problems at the enterprise,

01:27:54.500 --> 01:27:56.500
then we can reduce this bonus a little.

01:27:56.500 --> 01:27:58.500
I think that bonuses should not be used

01:27:58.500 --> 01:28:00.500
in this case,

01:28:00.500 --> 01:28:02.500
except for certain private cases

01:28:02.500 --> 01:28:04.500
where the work of the company

01:28:04.500 --> 01:28:06.500
affects the results of the enterprise as a whole,

01:28:06.500 --> 01:28:08.500
for example, the technical director.

01:28:08.500 --> 01:28:10.500
The social package

01:28:10.500 --> 01:28:12.500
is the same as managers have,

01:28:12.500 --> 01:28:14.500
that is, it is common for the company,

01:28:14.500 --> 01:28:16.500
probably, the best is the cafeteria system,

01:28:16.500 --> 01:28:18.500
and, again,

01:28:18.500 --> 01:28:20.500
it should take into account

01:28:20.500 --> 01:28:22.500
the work of our employee

01:28:22.500 --> 01:28:28.500
at the enterprise and the result they have achieved.

01:28:28.500 --> 01:28:30.500
The next compensation plan

01:28:30.500 --> 01:28:32.500
is called the Clerc,

01:28:32.500 --> 01:28:34.500
and it is intended for the executive staff

01:28:34.500 --> 01:28:36.500
of the infrastructure units

01:28:36.500 --> 01:28:38.500
and our office,

01:28:38.500 --> 01:28:40.500
for secretaries,

01:28:40.500 --> 01:28:42.500
for assistant managers,

01:28:42.500 --> 01:28:44.500
and so on, for the office staff.

01:28:44.500 --> 01:28:46.500
The salary here, too,

01:28:46.500 --> 01:28:48.500
the ratio of the salary and bonus

01:28:48.500 --> 01:28:50.500
should be the same

01:28:50.500 --> 01:28:52.500
as in the previous case,

01:28:52.500 --> 01:28:54.500
that is, 70-80% of the salary

01:28:54.500 --> 01:28:56.500
will be the salary,

01:28:56.500 --> 01:28:58.500
and the rest of the bonus,

01:28:58.500 --> 01:29:00.500
which we can also use

01:29:00.500 --> 01:29:02.500
to encourage those

01:29:02.500 --> 01:29:04.500
who work well

01:29:04.500 --> 01:29:06.500
and punish those

01:29:06.500 --> 01:29:08.500
who make mistakes,

01:29:08.500 --> 01:29:10.500
and so on.

01:29:10.500 --> 01:29:12.500
There is no need

01:29:12.500 --> 01:29:14.500
for bonuses.

01:29:14.500 --> 01:29:16.500
The social package,

01:29:16.500 --> 01:29:18.500
yes, it should be,

01:29:18.500 --> 01:29:20.500
it can work according to the principle of the cafeteria,

01:29:20.500 --> 01:29:22.500
it may not work according to it.

01:29:22.500 --> 01:29:24.500
The minimum package,

01:29:24.500 --> 01:29:26.500
which is usually the food,

01:29:26.500 --> 01:29:28.500
the compensation of the transport fee,

01:29:28.500 --> 01:29:30.500
well, maybe some other expenses,

01:29:30.500 --> 01:29:32.500
and most of all,

01:29:32.500 --> 01:29:34.500
it should be tied to the experience

01:29:34.500 --> 01:29:36.500
of our employee,

01:29:36.500 --> 01:29:38.500
if we want to secure

01:29:38.500 --> 01:29:40.500
the employee for the enterprise.

01:29:40.500 --> 01:29:42.500
It is difficult to say

01:29:42.500 --> 01:29:44.500
about the results,

01:29:44.500 --> 01:29:46.500
probably not,

01:29:46.500 --> 01:29:48.500
because employees of this category

01:29:48.500 --> 01:29:50.500
rarely give specific results.

01:29:50.500 --> 01:29:52.500
Usually, they require,

01:29:52.500 --> 01:29:54.500
as we have already said,

01:29:54.500 --> 01:29:56.500
a certain amount of money.

01:30:00.500 --> 01:30:02.500
The next option

01:30:02.500 --> 01:30:04.500
of the compensation plan,

01:30:04.500 --> 01:30:06.500
we will call it progressive,

01:30:06.500 --> 01:30:08.500
is intended for sales managers

01:30:08.500 --> 01:30:10.500
of various categories,

01:30:10.500 --> 01:30:12.500
that is, those people who sell,

01:30:12.500 --> 01:30:14.500
sell actively,

01:30:14.500 --> 01:30:16.500
do not stand at the counter

01:30:16.500 --> 01:30:18.500
and do not wait for the buyer to turn to them,

01:30:18.500 --> 01:30:20.500
but look for the buyer,

01:30:20.500 --> 01:30:22.500
consult him,

01:30:22.500 --> 01:30:24.500
and then make a purchase.

01:30:24.500 --> 01:30:26.500
Here the situation will change dramatically.

01:30:26.500 --> 01:30:28.500
The base salary should be

01:30:28.500 --> 01:30:30.500
relatively small

01:30:30.500 --> 01:30:32.500
and be 30-50% of the reward.

01:30:32.500 --> 01:30:34.500
This is, so to speak,

01:30:34.500 --> 01:30:36.500
for securing the employee for the enterprise

01:30:36.500 --> 01:30:38.500
and supporting him in those situations

01:30:38.500 --> 01:30:40.500
when, for one reason or another,

01:30:40.500 --> 01:30:42.500
he did not trade too much.

01:30:42.500 --> 01:30:44.500
The bonuses are large,

01:30:44.500 --> 01:30:46.500
up to half,

01:30:46.500 --> 01:30:48.500
and according to individual

01:30:48.500 --> 01:30:50.500
or group results.

01:30:50.500 --> 01:30:52.500
The bonuses should,

01:30:52.500 --> 01:30:54.500
unlike the previous case,

01:30:54.500 --> 01:30:56.500
not be guaranteed

01:30:56.500 --> 01:30:58.500
and be reduced if a person

01:30:58.500 --> 01:31:00.500
has not achieved the results,

01:31:00.500 --> 01:31:02.500
but vice versa,

01:31:02.500 --> 01:31:04.500
not be guaranteed in any case,

01:31:04.500 --> 01:31:06.500
but be increased

01:31:06.500 --> 01:31:08.500
when our employees

01:31:08.500 --> 01:31:10.500
achieve the appropriate results.

01:31:10.500 --> 01:31:12.500
Please do not forget

01:31:12.500 --> 01:31:14.500
about the system of planning

01:31:14.500 --> 01:31:16.500
and the use of vouchers.

01:31:16.500 --> 01:31:18.500
There are no bonuses,

01:31:18.500 --> 01:31:20.500
but there are some sales managers

01:31:20.500 --> 01:31:22.500
who make up half of the company's income.

01:31:22.500 --> 01:31:24.500
And finally,

01:31:24.500 --> 01:31:26.500
the social package.

01:31:26.500 --> 01:31:28.500
Yes, it is good,

01:31:28.500 --> 01:31:30.500
useful, necessary,

01:31:30.500 --> 01:31:32.500
it helps, it supports,

01:31:32.500 --> 01:31:34.500
but it is the same as in the previous categories,

01:31:34.500 --> 01:31:36.500
although, of course,

01:31:36.500 --> 01:31:38.500
taking into account the achieved results.

01:31:38.500 --> 01:31:40.500
The next very simple

01:31:40.500 --> 01:31:42.500
compensation plan,

01:31:42.500 --> 01:31:44.500
we call it a business plan,

01:31:44.500 --> 01:31:46.500
is for trading agents

01:31:46.500 --> 01:31:48.500
and individual workers.

01:31:48.500 --> 01:31:50.500
The basic contribution

01:31:50.500 --> 01:31:52.500
is either not there at all

01:31:52.500 --> 01:31:54.500
or it is minimal.

01:31:54.500 --> 01:31:56.500
The payment is almost free,

01:31:56.500 --> 01:31:58.500
that is, a person receives a bonus

01:31:58.500 --> 01:32:00.500
because he has earned it.

01:32:00.500 --> 01:32:02.500
The bonus is the main part

01:32:02.500 --> 01:32:04.500
of his income.

01:32:04.500 --> 01:32:06.500
Bonuses are not needed.

01:32:06.500 --> 01:32:08.500
The social package is not necessary,

01:32:08.500 --> 01:32:10.500
most likely not needed,

01:32:10.500 --> 01:32:12.500
but I want to emphasize

01:32:12.500 --> 01:32:14.500
a small detail.

01:32:14.500 --> 01:32:16.500
If a company wants to secure

01:32:16.500 --> 01:32:18.500
these categories,

01:32:18.500 --> 01:32:20.500
it is necessary to pay special attention.

01:32:20.500 --> 01:32:22.500
They should be supported morally,

01:32:22.500 --> 01:32:24.500
they should be held competitions

01:32:24.500 --> 01:32:26.500
for the best, they should be honored,

01:32:26.500 --> 01:32:28.500
they should be shown their value

01:32:28.500 --> 01:32:30.500
for the enterprise,

01:32:30.500 --> 01:32:32.500
that the enterprise believes in them,

01:32:32.500 --> 01:32:34.500
the enterprise hopes for them.

01:32:34.500 --> 01:32:36.500
Otherwise, without such a moral support,

01:32:36.500 --> 01:32:38.500
as practice shows,

01:32:38.500 --> 01:32:40.500
the loyalty to the enterprise

01:32:40.500 --> 01:32:42.500
is sharply reduced by the employee.

01:32:42.500 --> 01:32:44.500
The employee should get a percentage

01:32:44.500 --> 01:32:46.500
of what he has done.

01:32:46.500 --> 01:32:48.500
He needs respect.

01:32:48.500 --> 01:32:50.500
This is the final part

01:32:50.500 --> 01:32:52.500
of our lesson.

01:32:52.500 --> 01:32:54.500
I will summarize the lesson

01:32:54.500 --> 01:32:56.500
and wish you all the best

01:32:56.500 --> 01:32:58.500
in the field of our common

01:32:58.500 --> 01:33:00.500
and difficult business

01:33:00.500 --> 01:33:02.500
of managing the staff.

01:33:02.500 --> 01:33:04.500
Thank you for your attention.